    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair, road-worthy condition and is ready to serve as a dependable daily driver for its next owner. The engine starts reliably and runs well, though it would benefit from a standard tune-up to reach peak performance. While the transmission shifts through all gears, you may notice it isn't as smooth as a newer model. The exterior shows typical signs of age, including some minor scratches and paint fading, and the interior has been well-used but remains functional. This is a solid choice for someone looking for an affordable, functional vehicle who doesn't mind a few cosmetic imperfections.",
