    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been a fantastic ride and is still in really solid shape\u2014it runs like a dream and has been well-cared for over the years. It's super clean and ready for its next owner to take it on some fun road trips! If you're looking for something reliable and comfy that won't break the bank, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
