      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist-spec example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 inline-six heritage. The naturally aspirated powerplant features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system, delivering a linear power band and a metallic 8,000-RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M Differential Lock. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings, while the hydraulic steering rack provides the unfiltered feedback modern racks lack. Mechanically sorted and ready for the apex, this is a driver-focused machine with the structural and powertrain integrity enthusiasts demand.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Clean title. Reliable engine. Interior clean. Minor exterior scratches. Inspection welcome.",
