    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and remains in impressive shape both inside and out. The exterior retains a deep, glossy shine, though a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper reflect its honest history on the road. Inside, the leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, while all electronic features\u2014including the premium sound system and dual-zone climate control\u2014function perfectly. Mechanically, it is sound; it comes with a complete service record, a recent oil change, and the tires have plenty of tread remaining. It drives smoothly, shifts crisply, and offers a quiet, refined cabin experience. This is a reliable, well-documented car ready for its next owner.",
