    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking to find a new home for this awesome ride! It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and still runs like a dream. It\u2019s in solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable car that still looks great on the road. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have! Shoot me a message if you want to come take it for a spin! \u2728",
