      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six utilizing individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS for a sharp 8,000 RPM redline. This example features the desirable 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural rigidity. The suspension maintains its factory-tuned damping characteristics, providing exceptional turn-in and lateral grip. A well-sorted driver\u2019s car for the serious purist.",
